# Self-hosted Noto Sans JP woff2 subsets (mkdocs theme).
# Path-fingerprinted by sha10 of the upstream gstatic URL → safe to
# cache 1y immutable. Access-Control-Allow-Origin enables cross-subdomain
# use (e.g. api.jpcite.com docs preview).
# Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin overrides the global same-site
# default so the same font subsets can hydrate the mkdocs preview rendered
# on api.jpcite.com (different eTLD+1 sub-resource).
/static/fonts/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin

# OG / Twitter PNGs + decorative WebP previews. PNG sources stay because
# the Twitter card scraper does not reliably resolve WebP. 1-day cache
